data.description: This 3-bed, 2-bath home boasts 1,649 square feet with an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, and a cozy fireplace in the living room. The wrap around kitchen with breakfast nook has plenty of counter and cabinet space. Equipped with indoor laundry. Down the hall you will find generously sized guest bedrooms with large closets for all your storage needs. The master bedroom is spacious, providing an expansive retreat for relaxation and personal space. The ensuite has his and her sinks with a built in vanity and walk in shower. Enter your own private backyard oasis! Beautiful crystal blue pool to enjoy. With owned solar you'll have the ideal blend of comfort and energy efficiency. Dive into the good life today!
